  <brief_title>Sedation Protocols and Skeletal Muscle Metabolism in Mechanical Ventilated Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Different Sedation Protocols on Skeletal Muscle Metabolism in Mechanical Ventilated Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
