  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the effects of different sedation protocols on skeletal muscle metabolism in
      mechanical ventilated patients in ICU. Mechanical ventilated patients who are anticipated to
      stay in ICU for more than 5 days are enrolled and randomly assigned to the following three
      groups, interventional group(dexmedetomidine), control group(midazolam) and no sedation
      group. Serum, CT scan of intercostal muscles, ultrasound evaluation of quadriceps femoris are
      obtained.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
